entries.femaleVariant: Hah, your eyes are fucked up, man! Hah hah!
This's Li'l China, choom. It's too loud for ya, just slot in some earplugs and it's nighty-night.
What then, the smell? Sure, you're in that room like sardines, but fifteen minutes an' you barely notice it...
One guy in the room... Choom, he died.
Gray-hair guy, slept under all them rags... We thought he was sick or somethin'... But then we opened his sleepin' bag and phewww... blechh.
